{margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 23.0px; font: 16.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p12 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} span.s1 {font: 16.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #393939} span.s4 {font: 14.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #393939} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24919.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Levi's 宣布 2018 年度全新代言人陈伟霆</b></a>，发布了一支陈伟霆热舞的视频《新年严禁放嘴炮》，还做了个明星来电的 H5。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103115654Gr47MqZCswhaYvBN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.304000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/02/the-new-year-tvc-of-telunsu-milk/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>特仑苏在官方微博宣布全新代言人靳东</b></a>，并发布了一支靳东和另一位代言人陈道明共同出演的广告片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=w05271cmfeg&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://socialbeta.com/t/jiafangyifang-news-20170102\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>冈本和饿了么合作在上海开设的“时光便利店”</b></a>，店里贩售 600 颗时间胶囊，可以用来兑换冈本、饿了么会员卡、单向历、定制雨衣等等。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103121118VtWHJRL86I2dmDzU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665364\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103121127xMpNmskuIlRtwDaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665364\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103121138IhDzS0gCqoyNjxiU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p><b><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/02/netease-music-2017-users-data-came-out/\" rel=\"nofollow\">网易云音乐听歌日记刷屏</a>，除了&nbsp;</b>H5 网易云音乐还放出了一支彩蛋——《2018，音乐的力量》，风格延续了 2017 年 7 月推出的年度品牌篇《音乐的力量》。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=t05278vheze&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24877.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Nike 发布了欧文第四代签名战靴 “kyrie 4” 的广告片</b></a>，用一种较为轻松的方式，回应了此前欧文因和队友不和转投东部死敌凯尔特人队传闻。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103120307afyLNCckzujWt5rP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.518750\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24927.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>杜蕾斯也用一张长图文总结 2017</b></a>，如此正经的画风也是难得一见。点击链接查看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103120550415ulpFjvUrzoPQg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.792754\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/02/the-new-tvc-of-cmbchina-in-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>招商银行发布 2018 全新品牌形象大片</b></a>，主题是不同阶段的人生选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=a0527gagk06&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/modern-life-too-much-for-you-maybe-a-tiny-box-in-the-woods-is-the-cure/2017/12/27/f63de86a-e5ae-11e7-ab50-621fe0588340_story.html?hpid=hp_hp-more-top-stories-2_tinyhome-1p%3Ahomepage%2Fstory&amp;utm_term=.4339d069e335\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国的露营地林中小屋 Getaway，</b></a>主打治愈和逃离，除了提供把手机锁起来的箱子以及不提供 wifi，还在宣传广告中重点传递“睡眠”信息。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103120739XNAWp4uiRjJfPV7q.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667539\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://socialbeta.com/t/jiafangyifang-news-20170102\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>QQ 浏览器为“兴趣世界狂欢节”推出营销活动</b></a>，除了线上的 H5 等，还包括北京 798 一个废弃美术馆里的展览“兴趣招领处”，收集了 99 个丢弃兴趣的故事进行展示。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103120812k4TMq0JQxtCFNP1W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.859438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>最后，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/02/didi-chuxing-appoints-zenith-as-media-aor-in-mainland-china/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>滴滴出行宣布阳狮集团旗下实力媒体（Zenith）为其在中国大陆的独家媒介代理伙伴</b></a>，新的代理合约将覆盖传统媒体和数字媒体的媒介策划及购买业务。实力媒体会组建一支名为 “D+Z” 的服务团队，为滴滴出行提供“量身定制”的媒介服务。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://adage.com/article/digital/snapchat-considers-making-users-sit-3-seconds-ads/311775/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Snapchat 正在考虑给广告加上 3 秒钟时长的强制观看。</b></a>一位大广告商声称，Snapchat 上的广告平均观看时长甚至不到 1 秒，因为它们都太容易跳过了，只需要轻轻一滑。据称，Snapchat 的广告销售团队正在给内部高管施加压力，希望批准新的广告格式。<br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：饿了么</p>"}